mappings.messageTemplate:
Fireflies webhook received. A new meeting transcript is ready.

Webhook payload: {{json}}

Use the Fireflies API to fetch the full transcript using the meetingId. Then extract: decisions, action items (with owners and deadlines), blockers, scope changes, and open questions. Write the structured meeting note to the Meeting Notes database in Notion. Create tasks in the Sprint Board for each action item (status: Backlog). Post a summary to Slack.
